úA quiet place to sit and remember
Deborah Gillibrand
3rd June 1960 - 5th April 2018
Kind, caring and endlessly patient
Fun loving, generous and always smiling
when with your colleagues
And always giving your family and friends your unconditional love.
It's hard to forget someone who gave us so much to remember
With much love from all of us
